data.message: Font pairing patterns that work: (1) Sora + IBM Plex Mono = Japanese-Swiss minimal, (2) Inter + JetBrains Mono = Terminal/industrial dark, (3) Cormorant Garamond + Inter = Luxury elegant, (4) Bricolage Grotesque + DM Sans = Playful friendly, (5) IBM Plex Sans solo = Warm humanist organic. Use negative letter-spacing (-1 to -3px) on large headlines for premium density.
